; ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
; read_controllers - Read both NES controllers
; Strobes the controller port, then reads 8 bits from each controller.
; Handles DPCM bit-deletion bug by reading each bit twice and ORing.
; Filters out simultaneous opposing directions on d-pad.
